::Shadow Wing::
She saw that one bot inparticular was geting fired on.  Using her telescopic 
vision, she saw Cyber Claw getting the wiring beat out of her.  She wasn't 
sure about what faction Cyber Claw was, but she didn't like the odds.  Three 
to one is a bit uneven, she thought.
"Maybe I can help even up the odds a little."
She swooped down and screached at Cyber Claw, "GET DOWN!"
Shadow Wing swooped down and dive bombed the other Preds and shot at them 
with her optic lazars.  She didn't climb out of the dive right away, but 
flew right past Cyber Claw.
"Move it if you want to live."
She flapped her wings and flew through the trees and climbed back into the 
air for a second round.

>Cyber Claw bared her teeth as she saw the Predacons open fire on her. She
>lifted herself into the air, shifted herself to the right. Two shots,
>including missiles went by her. As she raised her arm to fire back with a
>mini missile that layed underneath her forearm, she was hit on the left
>shoulder by a signature seaking missile. She was thrown to the ground. The
>spikes on her shoulder shattered off of her, falling to the ground like
>shattering glass.
>
>She growled from the shot, trying to move. She had to move before they
>killed her. She made herself crawl. She looked back to the group.
>
>"You think I'm a Maximal. I am not. I am one of you. Sadly that it sounds."
>She stood up.
